{"tid":191530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法醫鼻鼾？","createTime":"2017-04-08T03:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T04:42:23.000Z","uid":29156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61e6fdd575f98fe390ce691af2bd9106e7fef0bd","tid":191530,"uid":29156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"有鼻鼾其實真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同人去旅行扯鼻鼾<br />\n嘈到人訓教第二朝比人屌又西面<br />\n但其實自己唔想又控制唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入黎一齊探討下有咩方法救救佢"},{"pid":"7564bdf6e0b740ae8eb0de5c04b425135fa27748","tid":191530,"uid":29156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:34:34.000Z","msg":"我打頭陣先啦<br />\n試過萬寧買個隻鼻貼<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DO719r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DO719r.jpg&h=d3ee3f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完全無用加垃圾 兩下就甩<br />\n之後上網睇分析鼻鼾成因好大關個口因為訓覺時肌肉鬆弛而打開導致呼呼唔暢順 於是去watsons買左隻鼻鼾牙扥 $500個隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YU7AMU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4YU7AMU.jpg&h=8f314401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n戴落訓明顯lock戴左個口等有個位可以呼吸 令到鼻鼾明顯少左 但問題係戴完第二朝個口同牙痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常人無可能堅持到日日戴 就算日日戴都可能整傷 都只係一個短期方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"256fdfb54154140c8c58da8467c1f52b3a30735b","tid":191530,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:39:09.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"494b79bd1f5edc99be8acb631f771a6dcc9615d2","tid":191530,"uid":36010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F420KW0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF420KW0.jpg&h=0ed9ef34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f737396f6b5e71706d384b9b08928ba92c001944"